name: Garbage Go - City Cleaning Simulator
summary: Garbage Go puts you in charge of cleaning up the city! Drive different trucks to collect trash and sweep the streets, making every area spotless. Explore different parts of the city, taking on tasks that keep everything tidy. With straightforward gameplay and a focus on fun, this game lets you experience the important job of keeping the city clean. Take the wheel, navigate the city, and make it shine in Garbage Go!
